items.content_html:
I became interested in Circuit Board design and I wanted to learn how to make my own circuit boards. So after a few days of learning, and a few weeks of waiting, my first circuit board has arrived!

It doesn't look like much, and there is a lot of wasted space on the board, but for my first design I think it looks pretty good!
